items.sentence: You may have been the last person to see Tom.
You didn't see this one coming, did you, Tom?
You know I can't wait for you if you're late.
You have to be prepared for whatever happens.
You aren't as beautiful as you think you are.
You should brush your teeth after every meal.
You won't find it so easy to do that anymore.
You shouldn't always believe what others say.
You might be able to talk to Tom later today.
You shouldn't tell children things like that.
